summary:
Aylin is an energetic & passionate marketing professional with engineering background who is determined to deliver results while leading the way to empower and enabling connections for success. 

Aylin has 19+ years of professional experience with multinational companies across three countries (Turkey, Italy & The Netherlands) and regional roles (Western Europe & Europe). Two relocations and her passion around languages and cultures made her become multi-lingual (Turkish, English, French, Italian and Dutch). Another passion of her is Diversity, Equity and Inclusion. She has been active and volunteering on many projects around this field.

She currently leads Marketing & Communications for Lineage Logistics in Europe. Lineage Logistics is the world’s leading temperature-controlled industrial REIT and logistics solutions provider. It has a global network of over 400 strategically located facilities totaling over 2 billion cubic feet of capacity, which spans 20 countries across North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific. www.lineagelogistics.com
